            "title": "LXC container directory related",
            "summary": "Default: /var/cache/lxc Ref: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25286546/change-lxc-container-directory ",
            "content_html": "<p>Default: /var/cache/lxc</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code>lxc.lxcpath</code> in <code>/etc/lxc/lxc.conf</code>, consult <code>man lxc.system.conf</code> for details.</li>\n<li><code>lxc-*</code> tools accepts <code>-P</code> flag to specify alternate container path.</li>\n<li><code>lxc-create</code> <code>-B dir</code> backing store has optional <code>--dir ROOTFS</code> flag.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Ref: <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25286546/change-lxc-container-directory\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25286546/change-lxc-container-directory</a> </p>",
